These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, blend, havana
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, chinese, spanish
1. the chinese is the blend-smoker##1
2. the havana-smoker is between the spanish and the blend-smoker##2
3. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Cigar      | blend | havana | siglo |
| Nationality   | chinese     | indonesian    | spanish   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, gospel, metal
City: liverpool, venice, hamburg
1. the fan salsa is on the left of the fan metal##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to liverpool and the fan salsa##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | metal        | gospel |
| City     | venice | hamburg | liverpool         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, ritmeester, prince
3 different games are played: chess, canasta, backgammon
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
2. the vegafina-smoker is between the person playing canasta and the prince-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | vegafina     | prince |
| Game        | canasta  | backgammon | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, australian, colombian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, swisher, bluemaster
1. the polish is the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the colombian is between the swisher-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##2
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Nationality   | australian  | colombian     | polish |
| Cigar           | swisher | bluemaster | tiparillo |

