.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
City: hamburg, miami, edinburgh
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, june, july
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in june##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| City   | miami | edinburgh     | hamburg |
| Birthday     | july    | november | june    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
House: futuristic, townhouse, ranch-style
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, march
1. the person who's birthday is in april is between the ranch-style house and the futuristic house##2
2. the futuristic house is the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| House   | futuristic  | townhouse   | ranch-style        |
| Birthday         | december | april | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, project-manager
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, tram, train
1. the project-manager is on the right of the fisherman##1
2. the person driving the boat is between the project-manager and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job          | lawyer  | fisherman  | project-manager |
| Transport   | tram | boat | train     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower, bellflower
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, iced-tea, juice
1. the person who growssunflower is the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who growssunflower and the person who growsbellflower##2
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Flower   | bellflower   | begonia  | sunflower  |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | iced-tea | juice |

