.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
City: venice, marseilles, new-york
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, purple, chestnut
1. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person who likes ebony is between the person traveling to new-york and the person who likes purple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| City       | new-york | venice | marseilles  |
| Color   | chestnut    | ebony        | purple |

