.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, tennis
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, light-blue, purple
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is between the person who likes purple and the person who's sport is rugby##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Sport         | tennis | surfing | rugby |
| Color   | purple     | brown    | light-blue |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, crime, fantasy
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, trance, funk
1. the fan funk is between the person watching crime movies and the fan indie##2
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | mystery      | fantasy      |
| Music-Genre       | trance  | funk | indie |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
