1. the person who growslily is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Flower   | bellflower | lily   | daisy   |
| Beverage         | fanta | hot-chocolate | lemonade |

