.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, december, july
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, sailing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's sport is sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |
| Birthday   | february | july | december |
| Sport     | sailing    | golf    | tennis |

