.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-15::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, traveling, camping
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person driving the boat is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
| Hobby   | traveling  | rock-climbing   | camping  |
| Transport        | snowmobile | boat | taxi |

