.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, cooking, fishing
House: modern, wooden, gothic-revival
1. the modern house is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | cooking | traveling   | fishing   |
| House         | gothic-revival  | modern | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-17::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, goldfish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, ambient, jazz
1. the owner of the goldfish is between the fan ambient and the owner of the turtle##2
2. the fan jazz is on the left of the fan ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |      3      |
| Pet   | turtle       | goldfish | ferret |
| Music-Genre         | country | jazz | ambient      |

