.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-18::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: superhero, musical, action
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, board-games, reading
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person watching action movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero       | musical    | action     |
| Hobby   | board-games | reading | magic-tricks |

