.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-19::.
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, cauliflower, lemon
City: hannover, london, hamburg
1. the person eating lemon is between the person traveling to hannover and the person eating nectarine##2
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
