.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
City: rome, london, new-york
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, nigerian, canadian
1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to new-york and the nigerian##2
3. the italian is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| City      | new-york | london   | rome |
| Nationality   | canadian  | italian | nigerian   |

 